The evidence with the title 'The federal health care law: what came true and what didn't | PolitiFact ' says Mar 20, 2015  ... Last year , the GOP seized on a talking point that 2.3 million jobs would go away because of the health care law . But that, too, was a misreading of evidence. A nonpartisan report actually showed that some people would stop working if they no longer had to work for insurance . PolitiFact rated the claim  ... 
